data.description: Beautiful all brick home located in Dogwood Hills. Great outdoor space! Many upgrades/improvements to include Refinished Hardwood Flooring in all Bedrooms and Living area, New Vinyl Flooring in Den, Kitchen/Dining area and Basement, Crown molding in all rooms, built in Stove and Microwave in the Kitchen, Refinished Laundry Room with accent wall and tabletop. Large Circular driveway to accommodate parking needs. The unfinished part of the basement has a workshop and outside entrance. Come and see this maintained and well cared for move in ready home!
